  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting at 14th level, you take advantage of the years of work in the field, between store shelves and the markets in the big cities, to enter and leave every place accompanied by interesting goods. If you need to hide an object, you can add 1d6 to the check, thanks to tricks of the trade.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Once during a narrative sequence focused on sneaking in or out of a place, you can use a bonus action to achieve automatic success.</span> </p>",
